subject: [ANN] Java Gui Builder 0.4a released !
msgSnippet: Hello all ! This new release brings a much needed reduction in the XML files verbosity. New elements combine old-style control+property elements into a single
messageBody:
Hello all !

This new release brings a much needed reduction in the XML files verbosity.
New elements combine old-style control+property elements into a single line.

You may download this new release at
http://sourceforge.net/project/showfiles.php?group_id=50316&release_id=95488

Thanks !

=====
Francois Beausoleil
Java Gui Builder - http://jgb.sourceforge.net/
